		(property "TEMPERATURA DE TRABAJO MíN." "-55°C<!--FANDB--><div class=\"features-and-benefits-container\"><div class=\"features-and-benefits-description\"><span class=\"features-benefits-value\">The Vishay D/CRCW e3 series are standard thick film chip resistors. The resistance range includes E96 and E24 decade values from 1ohm to 10Mohm. CRCW e3 series resistors have a pure tin solder contacts on the Ni barrier layer that provides compatibility with reflow soldering process.</span></div><div class=\"features-and-benefits-list\"><ul class=\"features-and-benefits-list-list\"><li class=\"features-and-benefits-list-item\">Automotive grade AEC-Q200 qualified</li><li class=\"features-and-benefits-list-item\">EIA 0402, 0603, 0805, 1206, 1210, 1218, 2010, 2512 standard case sizes available</li><li class=\"features-and-benefits-list-item\">Stability &Delta"
